Telekinetic Leap.name: Telekinetic Leap
Telekinetic Leap.flavor: You hurl yourself or one of your allies safely through the air using your mind.
keywords:
Ranged 10

Target: You or one ally

Effect: The target can fly up to 5 squares. If this power is used on an ally, that ally must remain in your line of sight at all times during the effect.
